public class MovielensElement
extends DatasetSparseVector<IntegerElement>

An element of the Movielens dataset.

A movielens element is a vector of ratings, and it can equally be a vector of ratings given by the same user on a set of movies or a vector of ratings on the same movies given by a set of users who rated it.
